                    <a href="https://calendar.google.com/calendar/render?action=TEMPLATE&text=13va.+Gran+Carrera+Celene&dates=20261017T070000/20261017T110000&ctz=America/Tijuana&details=Participa+en+la+13va+Gran+Carrera+con+Causa+de+Proyecto+Celene.+Registro+6:00+AM,+Salida+7:00+AM.&location=Pabellon+Rosarito" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-sports-secondary" style="background: white; border-color: var(--carrera-negro);">Agendar 🗓️</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="hero-image-container">
                <img src="https://i.ibb.co/q3tRY4DJ/carrera-13.png" alt="Corredora Proyecto Celene" class="hero-graphic">
